text: "Can't Hurt Me Now" is a song written by Fredrik Thomander and Aleena Gibson and performed by Jessica Andersson at Melodifestivalen 2015, where the song ended up 11th in the final. ==Chart positions== {|class="wikitable plainrowheaders sortable" style="text-align:center;" |- !align="left"|Chart (2015) !align="center"|Peak position |- |} == References == Category:2015 singles Category:2015 songs Category:Jessica Andersson songs Category:Melodifestivalen songs of 2015 Category:Songs written by Aleena Gibson Category:Songs written by Fredrik Thomander
